{
  "texts": [
    "Our review aimed to provide a preliminary snapshot of the state of the work on LLMs and games, to help researchers to understand the key directions and findings so far, and to lay the foundation for future work.",
    "We expect that capturing the state of the field and keeping pace with new research will be an ongoing challenge, but it is exciting to see where LLMs will take the field of games research and development.",
    "Manuscript submitted to ACM"
  ]
}